import ae.disk
import ae.disk.bot
import ae.network
import ae.network.bot
now = datetime.datetime.utcnow()
return [dawgie.schedule(ae.disk.task, ae.disk.bot.Engine(), dow=(now.
    weekday() + 1) % 7, time=now.time()), dawgie.schedule(ae.disk.task, ae.
    disk.bot.Engine(), dow=(now.weekday() - 1) % 7, time=now.time()),
    dawgie.schedule(ae.network.analysis, ae.network.bot.Analyzer(), boot=True)]
